Difference in Methylation

Measures of Variation across Sites

  • Variance of difference in methylation : Var(Xi)

  • Inter Quantile Range (IQR) : Q3 - Q1

  • Range of difference in Methylation : Max(X) - min(X)

  • Centralized variance of difference in methylation: Var(Xi - mu_j)

  • where Xi: Methylation values for subject i

  • mu_j : average of site j
